title: American Horror Story: Murder House Recap
author: GameSpot Universe
comment: We need some Tate and Violet and Kyle and Zoe moments again.
I know I’m not the only one who had the biggest crush on Tate 👀
I want Violet Back. I feel like the only one that liked her
I really wish jessica lange would come back.
As long as Taissa Farmiga, Jessica Lange, and Angela Bassett come back, I will be a happy camper.
